subject: Horse Racing
Breeders' Cup World Thoroughbred Championships
lead_paragraph: Still undefeated in four career starts, War Pass skipped over the Monmouth Park slop Saturday to run away from 11 rivals in the Breeders’ Cup Juvenile and leave no question unanswered.
